Show Description
................

From the Infowars web site :: On this live, Black Friday, November 29 edition of the Alex Jones Show, Alex and Infowars Nightly News host David Knight expose the continued zombiefication of America as stores across the country are ransacked by unruly mobs fighting for the latest in electronic slave goods. Yesterday, Knight and the crew interviewed consumers who had been waiting outside a local Best Buy since before dawn on Thanksgiving. Media analyst and political activist Mark Dice joins the broadcast to discuss his latest video in which he dressed up as Santa Claus and bullhorned shoppers who spent Thanksgiving waiting outside stores instead of being with their families at home. Paul Joseph Watson and Anthony Gucciardi also give their take on this zombie takeover of America.

This upload is the Prison Planet "members' edit," which has the commercials during scheduled breaks removed and the entire show in one MP3 file.
